                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">City Policeman</hi> 814). Gibson pointed out Bertram to me, who ran away; I ran after him, and caught him—he said, "Me no thief"—I saw Gibson pick the watch up; he gave it to me.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Bertram's Statement before the Magistrate</hi>:—"I wish to say I picked up the watch."</p>
